<s> To determine the depth of a node in the tree you can traverse the nodes returned by getParentNode() until the method returns null and count how many ancestors the node has.  </s>
<s> To determine the ordinal position of a node within its siblings you can do the same thing but call getPreviousSibling() instead of getParentNode().  </s>
