<s> To position a node in relation to the position of other elements, one can use the insertBefore() , getPreviousSibling() and getNextSibling() methods defined by the Node interface.  </s>
<s> As far as I know the DOM interfaces provide no method for retrieving the numerical value of the position of a node in a stucture implementing a NodeList.  </s>
